        {'instr':'Stay in the same notebook chat. Type the next prompt — Copilot remembers earlier prompts.', 'prompt':'Set the Instruction: "You are my chief of staff. Cite source file and tab/section for every recommendation. Use a RAG framework for all output." Then ask the Notebook which campaign ROI priorities appear underfunded or mis-sequenced given current results, and which priorities should be accelerated, deferred, or stopped. Require Notebook to present the answer as a RAG table with rationale and source citation per row.'},
        {'instr':'Stay in the same notebook chat. Type the next prompt — Copilot remembers earlier prompts.', 'prompt':'Set the Instruction: "You are my governance reviewer. Identify contradictions across the 3 sources and present concise pre-reads for the Executive Communications Review." Then ask the Notebook to identify where the strategy narrative, the operational reality, and the policy obligations are misaligned ahead of the Executive Communications Review. Request a concise answer with 3 sections: Contradictions to Resolve, Questions Directors Will Ask, and Recommended Pre-Reads, all with citation to the source file.'}
